title: NorthWood Tech And PUSH, Inc. Aim To Inspire Students With Hands-On Skills Day - DrydenWire
content: NorthWood Tech And PUSH, Inc. Aim To Inspire Students With Hands-On Skills Day  DrydenWire
description: Northwood Technical College is partnering with PUSH, Inc. to hold a ‘Hands-on Skills Day’ event on Thursday, May 5th.
